    <div class="tab-bd">
        <div id="hot-comments" class="tab">
            
    
        
        <div class="comment-item" data-cid="415186658">
            
    
    <div class="comment">
        <h3>
            <span class="comment-vote">
                <span class="votes">3305</span>
                <input value="415186658" type="hidden"/>
                <a href="javascript:;" class="j a_show_login" onclick="">有用</a>
            </span>
            <span class="comment-info">
                <a href="../../../https@www.douban.com/people/sickrain/default.htm" class="">坦克手贝吉塔</a>
                    <span>看过</span>
                    <span class="allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                <span class="comment-time " title="2011-07-17 23:58:29">
                    2011-07-17
                </span>
            </span>
        </h3>
        <p class="">
            
                <span class="short">作为东北工业区长大，工人家庭中的一员，看的过程中一直在流泪。砖墙、烟囱、下岗、厂房、硬碰硬、俄罗斯老歌、生锈的车间、失落的包工头、不卑不亢的父亲、埋在机床里的文艺梦，满含情怀，以及底层的、穷途末路似的智慧。一个阶级的倒掉，工厂之子的挽歌。比想象更荒诞的，是他们那个卑微的梦。</span>
        </p>
    </div>

        </div>
        
        <div class="comment-item" data-cid="374856343">
            
    
    <div class="comment">
        <h3>
            <span class="comment-vote">
